Class LogEventPredicate.AnyCondition

    LogEventPredicate
    public static class LogEventPredicate.AnyCondition
extends Object
implements LogEventPredicate
    A rule specifying that any log message will be logged if they must fulfill at least one of the specified conditions. This is used when there are multiple conditions that all should allow a message to be loaded
